<br>
The Pu239 is to be blended with uranium to create MOX nuclear reactor fuel and put it on the market.<br>
<br>
The downblend uranium fuel is immediately proliferation-resistant (altho the Pu produced from it in the reactor is not), but the MOX fuel will require safeguarding, and will be much more expensive to use.<br>
<br>
The Bush Administration decided not to dispose of Pu239 at Yucca Flats, but to sell it as fuel.<br>
